            <h3><b>IxTheo Open Text Service</b></h3>
            <p>With this extensive service, the FID Theologie assesses the legal situation and takes care of the cataloguing and the digitization of each publication. The publications are then freely accessible and searchable in IxTheo from across the world.</p>
	        <p>We offer this service to academics and researchers in Germany, Austria and Switzerland on the basis of German copyright law. Researchers could apply for a new phase of the Open Text Service in 2023.</p>

